data.description: WOW.! THE SELLER IS OFFERING A SELLER’S CREDIT TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR TO BUY RATE DOWN! Welcome to this exquisite and lately updated 3-level townhome located in the well sought after PERRYWOOD community. This home features 3-bedroom at upper level with master bath with separate tub and standing shower and other full bath for other 2 large room to share. It has not too old carpet throughout. The entire interior has been freshly painted. The upper 2 level is complete with spacious kitchen, half bathroom, fireplace, and open dining room that flows into the living room. The lower level offers a separate family room, play area or office with a door leading to the rear yard with a new full bathroom. NEW FLOORING 2022, ROOF 3 YEARS, HVAC 4 YEARS, NEW STOVE AND MICROWAVE. The community amenities include pools, tennis, basketball and volleyball courts, tot lots and community trails. Your dream home awaits This ultra convenient location is right around the corner from 295, 198 and I-95 and a short drive to Ft Meade, NSA, NASA Goddard, BWI, Arundel Mills, FDA in Laurel, Annapolis Junction.
